# Toast 提示

轻量通知提示（类似 shadcn/sonner）。需要在应用根部挂载一次 `<TxToastHost />`，然后在任意位置调用 `toast()`。

## 基础用法

### Toast
挂载 host 后触发提示。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="ToastToastDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxToastHost />
    <TxButton @click="toast({ title: 'Saved', description: 'Your changes have been saved.' })">
      Show toast
    </TxButton>
    <TxButton
      style="margin-left: 8px;"
      @click="toast({ title: 'Success', description: 'Done', variant: 'success' })"
    >
      Success
    </TxButton>
  </template>
---
:::
## API

### toast(options)

::TuffCodeBlock{lang="ts"}
---
code: |
  toast({
    title?: string
    description?: string
    variant?: 'default' | 'success' | 'warning' | 'danger'
    duration?: number // ms, 0 = 不自动关闭
  })
---
::

### dismissToast / clearToasts

从 `@talex-touch/tuffex/utils` 导入：

::TuffCodeBlock{lang="ts"}
---
code: |
  import { dismissToast, clearToasts } from '@talex-touch/tuffex/utils'
---
::
